 stages.\nWhen you get stuck, make use of a hint.\n\nStages:\nThere are 15 levels, and a total of 750 stages.\nAt first, it starts off with simple shapes, but each time your level increases, the number of lines increases, and it gets more and more complicated.\nYou might think it's too easy early on.\nHowever, clearing the simple stages is also important.\nThe hints to clearing the later, more complicated stages can all be found scattered through the simple stages.\n\nSome unique types of line, such as \"one way lines\" and \"overlapping lines\", can also be found throughout the stages.\nThese special lines will encourage your imagination.\n\nUse this chance to activate your mind as you play, by trying to solve this free-to-play brain-training puzzle game.\nYou're sure to get hooked!!","rating":90.0,"popularity":1.0,"total_rating":90.0,"total_rating_count":0,"rating_count":0,"games":[19222,41348,10225,27266,14246,60044,236,27725,101980,101976],"tags":[268435465],"category":0,"genres":[9],"first_release_date":1496102400000,"platforms":[39],"release_dates":[{"category":0,"platform":39,"date":1496102400000,"region":8,"human":"2017-May-30","y":2017,"m":5}],"screenshots":[{"url":"//images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_thumb/skhex7co4jiavitxgnnp.jpg","cloudinary_id":"skhex7co4jiavitxgnnp","width":552,"height":414},{"url":"//images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_thumb/wvpnvw5pvp7emdnlkaff.jpg","cloudinary_id":"wvpnvw5pvp7emdnlkaff","width":552,"height":414},{"url":"//images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_thumb/m9drutpfsa71vkcdoz7d.jpg","cloudinary_id":"m9drutpfsa71vkcdoz7d","width":552,"height":414},{"url":"//images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_thumb/nydobsh5fjicfb0fkw2a.jpg","cloudinary_id":"nydobsh5fjicfb0fkw2a","width":392,"height":696},{"url":"//images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_thumb/ryv7upzqmi5ilxsehtq2.jpg","cloudinary_id":"ryv7upzqmi5ilxsehtq2","width":392,"height":696},{"url":"//images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_thumb/emx0h3lmdpnyn1jbnqha.jpg","cloudinary_id":"emx0