or crafting. The recipes are organized and easily accessible. You can craft dozens of different items: building blocks for houses, furniture, decorations, weapons, armor, ammunition, and food for your dwarves.\n\nRTS\nAt the outset you find the recipes for basic tools and items, and build a small house with places to sleep and eat. Then, the size of the tribe increases and catches the attention of other inhabitants of the world. Most of them are night creatures and dwell underground. The worlds are full of fantasy creatures like zombies, skeletons, goblins, beholders, ghosts, giant spiders, and others. Some of them pay little attention to the dwarves, as long as the dwarves do not come into their field of vision. Others gather into quite large groups and try to break into the dwarves’ residence.\n\nTOWER DEFENSE\nEspecially dangerous are the waves of monsters that appear from time to time from portals. So, do not neglect to build a safe haven with strong walls and numerous trapdoors, cells, firing towers, and secret passageways.\n\nMAGIC\nAs a divine being, you possess various spells. You can speed up the movement of the dwarves, open small portals, illuminate dark caves to scare away monsters, evoke natural magic in the form of rain or tree growth, hurl fireballs at the monsters’ heads, and find useful resources and hidden rooms underground, thereby helping to speed up resource extraction, exploration of the world, and the population growth of your assistants.","rating":90.0,"popularity":1.0,"total_rating":90.0,"total_rating_count":0,"rating_count":0,"category":0,"genres":[12,13],"first_release_date":1418342400000,"platforms":[39],"release_dates":[{"category":0,"platform":39,"date":1418342400000,"region":8,"human":"2014-Dec-12","y":2014,"m":12}],"screenshots":[{"url":"//images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_thumb/kqzwdxiyazwwpsisguvn.jpg","cloudinary_id":"kqzwdxiyazwwpsisguvn","width":552,"height":414},{"url":"//images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_thumb/nhfpwihqa7ind