 board size up to 19x19\n- Track level per user\n- Computer resigns when too far behind (can be turned off)\n- Territory estimator\n- Hint\n- Undo\n- Replay\n- Tutorial with over 100 problems\n\nSmartGo Player is optimized for a quick and challenging game of Go against the computer. SmartGo Kifu is designed as a versatile tool for Go players who want to study professional games, practice Go problems, record their games, as well as play against the computer.\n\nEnjoy!","rating":50.0,"popularity":1.0,"total_rating":50.0,"total_rating_count":0,"rating_count":0,"games":[11362,9760,33603,36962,55888,73075,65827,2015,32283,75065],"tags":[268435471,536872273],"category":0,"keywords":[1361],"genres":[15],"first_release_date":1241568000000,"platforms":[39],"release_dates":[{"category":0,"platform":39,"date":1241568000000,"region":8,"human":"2009-May-06","y":2009,"m":5}],"screenshots":[{"url":"//images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_thumb/rvhnweslocedscpymmro.jpg","cloudinary_id":"rvhnweslocedscpymmro","width":552,"height":414},{"url":"//images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_thumb/ll6bmivfho29hf3du5i3.jpg","cloudinary_id":"ll6bmivfho29hf3du5i3","width":552,"height":414},{"url":"//images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_thumb/zngrx7imot5nevlnzrph.jpg","cloudinary_id":"zngrx7imot5nevlnzrph","width":552,"height":414},{"url":"//images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_thumb/ha8jxyel0tykq9tcelrr.jpg","cloudinary_id":"ha8jxyel0tykq9tcelrr","width":392,"height":696},{"url":"//images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_thumb/lefacnd9ed3tccekgtuq.jpg","cloudinary_id":"lefacnd9ed3tccekgtuq","width":392,"height":696},{"url":"//images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_thumb/sfh2ibhpcwrfz2elqm93.jpg","cloudinary_id":"sfh2ibhpcwrfz2elqm93","width":392,"height":696},{"url":"//images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_thumb/pevbrmlsrfwxywfr2cx1.jpg","cloudinary_id":"pevbrmlsrfwxywfr2cx1","width":392,"height":696}],"cover":{"url":"//images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_thumb/zc8uysuqkmovg4tmv2mg.jpg","cloudinary_id":"zc8uys