round terrors.\n\n• Nine legendary heroes. Choose your champions and train their abilities!\n\n• Special units and features on every stage! Watch out for the Black Dragon!\n\n• Merciless boss fights! Hey, we told you to get those upgrades...\n\n• Hours of gameplay with over 70 achievements!\n\n• Classic, Iron, and Heroic game modes to challenge your tactical skills!\n\n• Three difficulty modes! Are you up for a real challenge? Go with Hard mode!\nIntoxicating charm with a rousing score, full-bodied voice-overs and lovingly illustrated cartoon art! (Complete with cartoon blood, naturally.)\n\n• In-game encyclopedia! True warriors know thine enemies... and their towers. Study up!\n\nPRAISE FOR KINGDOM RUSH: IGN Editor's Choice, Slide To Play Must Have, 148 Apps Editor's Choice, Jay is Games Game of the Year, Pocket Gamer Gold Award, Touch Arcade 4.5/5, CNET. Best iPad Games","rating":80.0,"popularity":1.0,"total_rating":80.0,"total_rating_count":1,"rating_count":1,"games":[95340,34024,86605,103298,25311,76253,44102,84013,36608,87728],"tags":[1,268435471],"category":0,"themes":[1],"genres":[15],"first_release_date":1370476800000,"platforms":[39],"release_dates":[{"category":0,"platform":39,"date":1370476800000,"region":8,"human":"2013-Jun-06","y":2013,"m":6}],"screenshots":[{"url":"//images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_thumb/tsaoimoirs0pjl62uby3.jpg","cloudinary_id":"tsaoimoirs0pjl62uby3","width":552,"height":414},{"url":"//images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_thumb/d0axremmo0prhczx5zrc.jpg","cloudinary_id":"d0axremmo0prhczx5zrc","width":552,"height":414},{"url":"//images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_thumb/zbuysk2jojctmpc6btzh.jpg","cloudinary_id":"zbuysk2jojctmpc6btzh","width":552,"height":414},{"url":"//images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_thumb/hugnvmppj6ackt7nakvc.jpg","cloudinary_id":"hugnvmppj6ackt7nakvc","width":552,"height":414},{"url":"//images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_thumb/cxs2oslqgssrrjwichtq.jpg","cloudinary_id":"cxs2oslqgssrrjwichtq","width":552,"height