driving model. You can customize various elements of your trucks, from mechanical like gearboxes and engines to visual like wheels, fenders, exhausts and other\nchrome goodness- you are limited only by your imagination!. Feel free to create a powerful truck of\nyour dreams and compare your designs to those of your friends.\n\nSick and tired of repetitive tasks? That is no longer an issue! In Truck Simulator PRO 2 you will\nexperience realistic quests of a professional driver – like delivering timber to sawmills or heavy\nmachinery to road works. Hundreds of missions to accomplish will keep you occupied for a long\nperiod of time!\n\nFeatures:\n▶ 8 trucks with different driving models that you can own, customize and upgrade\n▶ Variety of cargos to transport across a huge map covering the eastern half of USA\n▶ Over 30 different types of shipments/cargos to deliver\n▶ Breathtaking open world to explore\n▶ 12 big cities to visit\n▶ Realistic fuel consumption and fatigue system\n▶ Expanded customization\n▶ Hundreds of realistic quests\n▶ Detailed interior view for each truck","rating":80.0,"popularity":1.0,"total_rating":80.0,"total_rating_count":0,"rating_count":0,"games":[44242,28465,34919,40470,33603,36962,55888,65827,75102,43130],"tags":[268435466,268435469],"category":0,"genres":[10,13],"first_release_date":1485993600000,"platforms":[39],"release_dates":[{"category":0,"platform":39,"date":1485993600000,"region":8,"human":"2017-Feb-02","y":2017,"m":2}],"screenshots":[{"url":"//images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_thumb/pth1xwqwoefwspjbqrrv.jpg","cloudinary_id":"pth1xwqwoefwspjbqrrv","width":552,"height":414},{"url":"//images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_thumb/grgljtp46aztqs5hoq9k.jpg","cloudinary_id":"grgljtp46aztqs5hoq9k","width":552,"height":414},{"url":"//images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_thumb/w0t1nqhxvsoqdfllbgaf.jpg","cloudinary_id":"w0t1nqhxvsoqdfllbgaf","width":552,"height":414},{"url":"//images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_thumb/ehiuiogrxxibobf8ykso.jpg","