 \nSpoken help is always just a tap away. Easy to learn, harder to master. \n\nView the gameplay video at www.trinogames.com, where you can also follow the development of new (free) updates!\n\n** #1 Game in Norway, Sweden, Austria, Switzerland and others. Top Simulation \u0026 Kids game in over 95 countries! **\n\n** Device recommendations and download info **\nRuns on all iPads! iPad second or third generation recommended for better graphics.\n\nMay require wifi connection to download.\n\n** Help us shape the future and help you **\nPlease get in touch! Request features or new vehicles! And let us know if you have any problems. We work for you! Just click the website/support link on this page.","rating":90.0,"popularity":1.0,"total_rating":90.0,"total_rating_count":0,"rating_count":0,"games":[44242,28465,34919,33603,36962,55888,65827,75102,43130,28277],"tags":[268435469,536872030],"category":0,"keywords":[1118],"genres":[13],"first_release_date":1326499200000,"platforms":[39],"release_dates":[{"category":0,"platform":39,"date":1326499200000,"region":8,"human":"2012-Jan-14","y":2012,"m":1}],"screenshots":[{"url":"//images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_thumb/lk5i2d5xlyoayy2sepx2.jpg","cloudinary_id":"lk5i2d5xlyoayy2sepx2","width":480,"height":360},{"url":"//images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_thumb/fwsdamtxdr0mg0pbi9ma.jpg","cloudinary_id":"fwsdamtxdr0mg0pbi9ma","width":480,"height":360},{"url":"//images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_thumb/map5jcssx1tbzrh9fjvz.jpg","cloudinary_id":"map5jcssx1tbzrh9fjvz","width":480,"height":360},{"url":"//images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_thumb/ubzl4jtavt5hhbuvvmad.jpg","cloudinary_id":"ubzl4jtavt5hhbuvvmad","width":480,"height":360},{"url":"//images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_thumb/eiwr74pysjct0yjamizq.jpg","cloudinary_id":"eiwr74pysjct0yjamizq","width":480,"height":360},{"url":"//images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_thumb/mxxdvpro7mysqzopcppe.jpg","cloudinary_id":"mxxdvpro7mysqzopcppe","width":405,"height":228},{"url":"//images.i