r hidden data collection. LEGO marketing content and information is served, for instance LEGO news about LEGO sets and other LEGO games, in hope of inspiring children’s creative play.\n\nWhy play with LEGO DC Super Heroes?\nLEGO DC Super Heroes Mighty Micros is a world full of your favorite classic heroes and villains, with a fun, creative LEGO twist. It’s empowering to play a hero, and it’s thrilling to play the bad guy when you know it’s just a game! We hope this game will inspire hours of role-play, both here, and in real life! Who knows, maybe you will discover what kind of hero YOU are along the way?\n\nFor app support contact LEGO Consumer Service. \nFor contact details refer to http://service.LEGO.com/contactus \n\nOur privacy policy and terms of use for apps are accepted if you download this app. \nRead more on http://aboutus.LEGO.com/legal-notice/Privacy-Policy and http://aboutus.LEGO.com/legal-notice/terms-of-use-for-apps \n\nLEGO, the LEGO logo, NINJAGO and the Minifigure are trademarks of the LEGO Group. ©2017 The LEGO Group.\nLEGO System A/S Website ---  LEGO® DC Super Heroes Chase app Support","rating":80.0,"popularity":1.0,"total_rating":80.0,"total_rating_count":0,"rating_count":0,"games":[23314,18699,102053,95095,91087,88819,88760,87729,87585,87282],"tags":[268435466,268435489],"category":0,"genres":[10,33],"first_release_date":1456790400000,"platforms":[39],"release_dates":[{"category":0,"platform":39,"date":1456790400000,"region":8,"human":"2016-Mar-01","y":2016,"m":3}],"screenshots":[{"url":"//images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_thumb/jthhb6gkhufwcdsozv5d.jpg","cloudinary_id":"jthhb6gkhufwcdsozv5d","width":552,"height":414},{"url":"//images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_thumb/zorpxtdnhfc76bupjei4.jpg","cloudinary_id":"zorpxtdnhfc76bupjei4","width":552,"height":414},{"url":"//images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_thumb/fzar9gb58h6iakdn3ypf.jpg","cloudinary_id":"fzar9gb58h6iakdn3ypf","width":552,"height":414},{"url":"//images.igdb.com/igdb/image/uploa