ps to build exclusively with friends or people you know\n•\tAbility to create read-only maps viewable to all players. But only you can modify them!\n•\tUpload your maps from Single player creative to Online Multiplayer server!\n•\tPlay cross platform with your friends (Apple App Store, Google Play, Amazon App Store, Mac App Store, Windows Store)\n•\tNo need to setup and/or host a server\n•\tNo subscription or additional fees required \n\nOUR FORUM: http://woc.solverlabs.com/forum\n\nCOMMUNITY SITE: http://woc.solverlabs.com/ \n\nYOUTUBE: http://www.youtube.com/user/WoCSolverlabs/\n \nFACEBOOK: http://www.facebook.com/worldofcubesonline \n\nTWITTER: http://twitter.com/WoCSolverlabs","rating":80.0,"popularity":1.0,"total_rating":80.0,"total_rating_count":0,"rating_count":0,"games":[43130,28277,41895,74378,25311,26145,44242,22425,28465,37419],"tags":[268435469,268435487],"category":0,"genres":[13,31],"first_release_date":1364342400000,"platforms":[39],"release_dates":[{"category":0,"platform":39,"date":1364342400000,"region":8,"human":"2013-Mar-27","y":2013,"m":3}],"screenshots":[{"url":"//images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_thumb/uovt67pmpczayozwpa5j.jpg","cloudinary_id":"uovt67pmpczayozwpa5j","width":552,"height":414},{"url":"//images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_thumb/yxpapiufe3tbfmadw1fx.jpg","cloudinary_id":"yxpapiufe3tbfmadw1fx","width":552,"height":414},{"url":"//images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_thumb/qunlq6anlefvm5sfyfkx.jpg","cloudinary_id":"qunlq6anlefvm5sfyfkx","width":552,"height":414},{"url":"//images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_thumb/jzg5uzaebzvlcnkoqcue.jpg","cloudinary_id":"jzg5uzaebzvlcnkoqcue","width":552,"height":414},{"url":"//images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_thumb/lssdbvfwkaki8easq6iy.jpg","cloudinary_id":"lssdbvfwkaki8easq6iy","width":552,"height":414},{"url":"//images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_thumb/vne9dqwxe76fitlwrww7.jpg","cloudinary_id":"vne9dqwxe76fitlwrww7","width":405,"height":228},{"url":"//images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_th