 family in the safety of a rock cavern. An incredibly large and beautiful world awaits you!\n\n3D ANIMATED VOXEL ANIMALS\nLoads of block-style animals with realistic animations bring the wild world of Wolf Craft to life! Wolves, foxes, deer, skunks, raccoons, snakes, fish, birds and more are waiting to challenge you!\n\nSIMULATED WEATHER AND ATMOSPHERE\nPlay all day and through the night and watch as the world changes around you! Twinkling stars and realtime sunsets add realism and beauty to your experience that to our Advanced Weather Simulator!\n\nNO ADS OR IN-APP PURCHASES\nDon’t worry about any bothersome ads popping up while your in a fight for your life!\n\nCraft your wolf and start the adventure of a lifetime today, the most unique crafting game in the world is finally here, Wolf Craft!","rating":90.0,"popularity":1.0,"total_rating":90.0,"total_rating_count":0,"rating_count":0,"games":[75102,49414,25636,74378,25311,26145,44242,75398,36608,28465],"tags":[268435468,268435469],"category":0,"genres":[12,13],"first_release_date":1434067200000,"platforms":[39],"release_dates":[{"category":0,"platform":39,"date":1434067200000,"region":8,"human":"2015-Jun-12","y":2015,"m":6}],"screenshots":[{"url":"//images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_thumb/womwftsbf2kfghdn3eyn.jpg","cloudinary_id":"womwftsbf2kfghdn3eyn","width":480,"height":360},{"url":"//images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_thumb/eldrpthsjugk9n5hbxxe.jpg","cloudinary_id":"eldrpthsjugk9n5hbxxe","width":480,"height":360},{"url":"//images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_thumb/hfxns6u7kh0dn4ym6ojt.jpg","cloudinary_id":"hfxns6u7kh0dn4ym6ojt","width":480,"height":360},{"url":"//images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_thumb/fqvcmz0t0yaurdyewohi.jpg","cloudinary_id":"fqvcmz0t0yaurdyewohi","width":480,"height":360},{"url":"//images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_thumb/yrcsiniref06hwfdaasy.jpg","cloudinary_id":"yrcsiniref06hwfdaasy","width":480,"height":360},{"url":"//images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_thumb/sf442ozxc7nubuss5vhp.jpg